---
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Ankit Garg"
	description="About Ankit Garg and the way he approaches quality leadership, delivery, and team collaboration."
>
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About Ankit"
				tagline="Ankit is the kind of Lead QA Engineer teams rely on when strong execution, operational quality, and healthy collaboration all matter at the same time."
				align="start"
			/>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Ankit Garg is a Lead QA Engineer whose reputation is grounded in reliable delivery,
						high standards, and the ability to work well with the people around him. A former
						teammate described him as consistently positive, supportive, and easy to collaborate
						with, which is a meaningful signal on any fast-moving product team.
					</p>
					<p>
						At Vimeo, he contributed to a high-profile product effort where the team maintained an
						exceptional quality bar for roughly two and a half years without a critical bug or
						rollback. That outcome speaks to discipline, thoughtful planning, and real ownership.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">How He Works</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Ankit stands out for how he combines execution with team health. He is described as
						approachable, generous with his time, and willing to help regardless of who reaches
						out. That kind of consistency improves collaboration and makes teams more resilient.
					</p>
					<p>
						He also brings structure and clarity to complex initiatives. Rather than relying on
						heroics, he helps work move forward through coordination, accountability, and steady
						follow-through.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">What He Brings</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>Integrity and self-motivation</li>
						<li>Dependable execution on high-visibility work</li>
						<li>Operational excellence and quality-minded delivery</li>
						<li>Thoughtful coordination that keeps teams aligned</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.content :global(ul) {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
	}

	.content :global(li + li) {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
